posting_body: ['M Street, managed by Holland Residential', '910 8th Avenue', 'Seattle, WA 98104', 'show contact info', 'VIEW OUR WEBSITE:', '<URL>', 'Located in the heart of Seattle, M Street apartments are within walking distance to some of the hottest night spots, restaurants and entertainment near First Hill and Seattle University.', 'Come by for a private tour.', 'Copy and Paste this link to view our screening criteria:', '<URL>', 'This two bedroom apartment features a spacious master suite with walk-in closet and private bathroom.', 'Huge open kitchen with kitchen island looking out into the living room!', 'windows throughout the kitchen and living room allowing tons of natural light in!', 'Enjoy some fresh air while out on your balcony and enjoy the views of the city!', 'This apartment requires a $525 deposit.', 'Community Features', '* Renters Insurance is Required', '* Easy Freeway Access', '* Community Lounge', '* Bark Park', '* Garage Parking', '* Reserved Parking', '* Controlled Access', '* Minutes from Restaurants, Shopping, and Much More', '*', "Our prices can change daily, price listed is based on today's availability.", 'Call for details.', '* Extra Storage', '* Controlled Access Parking', '* Resource Center', '* TV Lounge', '* Elevator', '* WiFi Access', '* Bike Racks', '* We are a social community!', 'Find our Yelp, Facebook or Twitter page online.', '* Professionally Managed', '* Outdoor Grill Area', '* Rooftop Terraces with Amazing Views', '* E-Lounge', '* After-Hours Emergency Maintenance', '* Easy Access to Public Transportation', '* Package Acceptance', '* Fitness Studio']
